Manchester United  forward  Wayne
Rooney  was charged by the Football Association with using
offensive language after cursing into a field-side television
camera during a 4-2 win at West Ham last weekend.  Rooney has until April 5 to respond to the charge,
according to a statement released today on the F.A. website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
